steps.name: Login With valid credentials
Click Workflow and click Receiving
Enter "SAMPLE-10" into Barcode search criteria and click Find button
Double-click search result
Click Search criteria and enter "SAMPLE-11" into Barcode search criteria and click Find button
Double-click search result again
Click OK button on the Find Assets to Receive screen
Click Department elipsis button and select "Quality Department"
Enter "Test_Location" and enter "3" and enter "Test_Contact"
Select "Mechanical" for Work Area
Select "One Time Only" for Reason for Service
Select "In Tolerance" for Initial Condition
Check On Site checkbox and check Expedite checkbox
Select second asset and verify the Department is blank
Verify Location is blank
Verify Work Area is "Electronic"
Verify Reason of Service is "Normal Cycle"
Verify Initial Condition is blank
Verify Quantity is "1" and Contact Info is blank
Verify On Site checkbox is unchecked
Verify Expedite checkbox is unchecked
Select first asset and check Location checkbox
Select second asset and verify Location is "Test_Location"
Select first asset and uncheck Location checkbox
Select second asset and verify Location is "Test_Location"
Select first asset and click Select button
Verify Department relative checkbox is checked and Location relative checkbox is checked
Verify Work Area relative checkbox is checked and Reason for Service relative checkbox is checked
Verify Initial Condition relative checkbox is checked and Priority relative checkbox is checked
Verify Quantity relative checkbox is checked and Job Number relative checkbox is checked
Verify On Site relative checkbox is checked and Expedite relative checkbox is checked
Verify ISOCert relative checkbox is checked and Service Type relative checkbox is checked
Verify Status relative checkbox is checked and Open Date relative checkbox is checked
Verify Required Date relative checkbox is checked and Category relative checkbox is checked
Verify Sub Category relative checkbox is checked and Contact Info relative checkbox is checked
Verify Required Date is Open Date plus 14 days
Enter "1" to Priority and verify Required Date is Open Date plus 3 days
Enter "2" to Priority and Verify Required Date is Open Date plus 7 days
Enter "3" to Priority and click Process button
cick OK on the Attention message and click Close button
